  <entry>
    <title>Three Scarlet Submarines (三艘深红潜艇)</title>
    <link href="https://chuishen.xyz/01/ThreeScarletSubmarines.html"/>
    <id>https://chuishen.xyz/01/ThreeScarletSubmarines.html</id>
    <published>2025-12-16T10:12:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-12-16T10:15:25.688Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Above the frigid seabed where the sunlight could not reach, Three Scarlet Submarines move slowly. Nothing could be seen in their windows other than the infinity of water and rocky edges. They were sent on a forgotten mission by a bureaucracy that ceased to exist shortly after the mission was given. Every aspect of their story could be debated. Except for the colour of the ships, perhaps, that’s why they were called “Three Scarlet Submarines.”&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
